avdta.dta

Class ReadDTANetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.network.ReadNetwork
      • avdta.demand.ReadDemandNetwork
        • avdta.dta.ReadDTANetwork
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MTReadNetwork, ReadFourStepNetwork

    public class ReadDTANetwork
extends ReadDemandNetwork
    This adds methods to read the trip table for DTA. This also contains the ReadDemandNetwork.prepareDemand(avdta.project.DemandProject, double) method to generate demand.

    • Method Detail

      • readNetwork

        public DTASimulator readNetwork(DTAProject project)
                         throws java.io.IOException
        Constructs a DTASimulator for the given DTAProject. This calls ReadNetwork.readNodes(avdta.project.Project) and ReadNetwork.readLinks(avdta.project.Project) and initializes the simulator (Network.initialize()). This also reads transit (ReadNetwork.readTransit(avdta.project.TransitProject) and personal vehicles (readVehicles(avdta.project.DTAProject)).
        Parameters:
        project - the DTAProject
        Returns:
        the created DTASimulator
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if a file cannot be accessed
